=== Capturing mock (recorded outputs) ===
[PASS] say: Hello, Carol!
[PASS] say: How are you today?
[PASS] ask prompt matched
Return value: You said: test input

=== Error injection mock ===
[mock] Greeting Dave
Result: Hello, Dave!
Result: ERROR: empty name

Key insight: greet_user never calls println directly.
The handler is the test harness. No test framework needed.
